<section style="font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><section class="" style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 15%; padding-right: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style=" text-align: center; margin: 10px 0%;  box-sizing: border-box; "><img style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/lZxqO3dCoYhjdM5Sv4IBPjDa9qZSCjItT1qgZcf8tT7oicOtsxsrLScbSHbcsLkjg9MTgz28WicPAzptpcLVbFibw/0?wx_fmt=png" class="" data-type="png" data-ratio="1.212686567164179" data-w="268"  /></section></section></section><section class="" style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 70%; box-sizing: border-box;"><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style=" margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0%; margin-left: 0%;  box-sizing: border-box; "><section class="" style="font-size: 19.25px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.4; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><br  /></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"  /></p></section></section></section></section><section class="" style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 15%; padding-left: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style=" text-align: center; margin: 10px 0%;  box-sizing: border-box; "><img style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/lZxqO3dCoYhjdM5Sv4IBPjDa9qZSCjItT1qgZcf8tT7oicOtsxsrLScbSHbcsLkjg9MTgz28WicPAzptpcLVbFibw/0?wx_fmt=png" class="" data-type="png" data-ratio="1.212686567164179" data-w="268"  /></section></section></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(67, 103, 117) 0px 0px 10px inset; box-sizing: border-box; background-image: url(&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/lZxqO3dCoYhjdM5Sv4IBPjDa9qZSCjItjmLHNgAMlcoIY5zE74Tso5TtCxYia8XcQPb9mPVD8qQ9nVAQZCx9tYA/0?wx_fmt=png&quot;); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: rgb(229, 241, 246); background-size: 87.8999%; background-position: 42.7805% 56.4516%; background-repeat: repeat;" class=""><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; "><section class="" style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; padding: 10px; border-radius: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style=" margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0%; margin-left: 0%;  box-sizing: border-box; "><section class="" style="text-align: center; color: rgb(84, 37, 92); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="box-sizing: border-box;">这是哈工大模联历史上的第一个中文委员会，让我们来带大家了解一下吧~</p></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style=" margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; text-align: center;  box-sizing: border-box; "><section class="" style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; min-width: 4.6em; max-width: 100%; height: 2.3em; border-radius: 3em 3em 0px 0px; border: 2px solid rgb(84, 37, 92); padding-top: 0.3em; padding-right: 0.3em; padding-left: 0.3em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section class="" style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; height: 100%; line-height: 1.6em; border-radius: 3em 3em 0px 0px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16.8px; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(84, 37, 92);"><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"  /></p></section></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style=" margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0%; margin-left: 0%;  box-sizing: border-box; "><section class="" style="text-align: center; color: rgb(84, 37, 92); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box;">1942年1月，在第二次世界大战之时，26个同盟国签署了现在《联合国宪章》的前身--《联合国家宣言》以彰显对同盟国抗战的支持。3年后的9月，战争结束。同年十月如今安理会的五大常任理事国（中华民国、美利坚合众国、大不列颠及北爱尔兰联合王国、法兰西第五共和国以及苏维埃社会主义共和国联盟。中华民国后由于解放战争暂时退出联合国，1971年以中华人民共和国身份重返联合国；苏联解体后俄罗斯接替其安理会席位。）以及其余46个国家签署了《联合国宪章》，此后，联合国作为一个实体组织正式出现。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"  /></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><br  /></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;">《联合国宪章》按规定设立六个联合国主要机构，安全理事会便是其中之一。《联合国宪章》将维护国际和平与安全的首要责任赋予安全理事会，安全理事会可在和平受到威胁时随时举行会议。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><br  /></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;">自1946年1月联合国安理会进行第一次会议，通过了安理会议事规则后，安理会宣告正式成立。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><br  /></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;">根据《联合国宪章》， 安全理事会负有维护国际和平与安全的首要责任。 安全理事会共有15个理事国，每一理事国有一票投票权。根据《联合国宪章》，所有理事国都有义务按要求履行安理会的决定。安全理事会会率先断定对和平有威胁或侵略的行为是否存在，促请争端各方以和平手段解决争端，并建议调整方案或解决问题的条件。在有些情况下，安全理事会可以实行制裁，甚至授权使用武力，以维护或恢复国际和平与安全。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;">其主要职能与权力有：</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;">1.依照联合国的宗旨和原则来维护国际和平与安全；</p></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style=" margin-right: 0%; margin-left: 0%;  box-sizing: border-box; "><section class="" style="text-align: center; color: rgb(84, 37, 92); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;">2.调查可能引起国际摩擦的任何争端或局势；</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;">3.建议调解这些争端的方法或解决条件；</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;">4.制定计划以处理对和平的威胁或侵略行为，并建议应采取的行动；</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;">5.促请各会员国实施经济制裁和除使用武力以外的其他措施以防止或制止侵略；</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;">6.对侵略者采取军事行动；</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><span style="line-height: 1.6;">7.就接纳新会员国以及各国加入《国际法院规约》的条件提出建议；</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;">8.在“战略地区”行使联合国的托管职能；</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;">9.就秘书长的任命向大会提出建议，并与大会共同选举国际法院的法官。</p></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style=" margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; text-align: center;  box-sizing: border-box; "><section class="" style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%; min-width: 4.6em; height: 2.3em; border-radius: 0px 0px 3em 3em; border: 2px solid rgb(84, 37, 92); padding-right: 0.3em; padding-bottom: 0.3em; padding-left: 0.3em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section class="" style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; height: 100%; line-height: 1.6em; border-radius: 0px 0px 3em 3em; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16.8px; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(84, 37, 92);"><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"  /></p></section></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style=" margin-right: 0%; margin-left: 0%;  box-sizing: border-box; "><section class="" style="text-align: center; color: rgb(84, 37, 92); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box;">那么，委员会的介绍至此就告一段落啦，下一期我们将走进具体议题，一起了解国际热点~</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"  /></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"  /></p></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style=" margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0%; margin-left: 0%;  box-sizing: border-box; "><section class="" style="text-align: center; color: rgb(84, 37, 92); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="color: rgb(84, 37, 92); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: right; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(229, 241, 246);"><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 12px; line-height: 19.2px;">李达夫 &nbsp;| &nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 12px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);">撰稿 </span></p><p style="color: rgb(84, 37, 92); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: right; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(229, 241, 246);"><span style="font-size: 12px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);"> 王若颖 周弘毅 沈一帆 张润泽 &nbsp;| &nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 12px; line-height: 19.2px;">审核</span></p><p style="color: rgb(84, 37, 92); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: right; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(229, 241, 246);"><span style="font-size: 12px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);">李汭虓 &nbsp;| &nbsp;编辑</span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style=" text-align: center; margin-right: 0%; margin-left: 0%;  box-sizing: border-box; "></section></section></section></section></section></section><section class="" powered-by="xiumi.us" style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><s